{"tid":1012795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 之前世界盃嗰個克羅地亞痴線佬被逐出境","createTime":"2019-02-08T00:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T09:57:53.000Z","uid":196258,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5158b6bd4c5ca460dec3fe2832cb26d4d33701","tid":1012795,"uid":196258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://slobodnadalmacija.hr/bbimagehandler.ashx?file=/Portals/0/Images/2019/02/02/kinezi.jpg&amp;width=780\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslobodnadalmacija.hr%2Fbbimagehandler.ashx%3Ffile%3D%2FPortals%2F0%2FImages%2F2019%2F02%2F02%2Fkinezi.jpg%26width%3D780&h=65547d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上星期六克羅地亞當地媒體出咗篇文，話南部邊境城鎮Imotski有個四十三歲中國人（同埋一個六十歲當地人）喺酒吧嗌克羅地亞法西斯口號，結果被捕同埋被控違反公眾安全條例，文中有FB片睇但當時未知後續如何<br />\n<br />\n篇文碌落去有片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://slobodnadalmacija.hr/dalmacija/split-zupanija/clanak/id/587269/drustvenim-mrezama-siri-se-snimka-na-kojoj-dvojica-kineza-u-imotskom-pjevaju-navijacke-i-uzvikuju-za-dom-spremni-policija-privela-43-godisnjaka-iz-kine-i-60-godisnjeg-hrvata\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslobodnadalmacija.hr%2Fdalmacija%2Fsplit-zupanija%2Fclanak%2Fid%2F587269%2Fdrustvenim-mrezama-siri-se-snimka-na-kojoj-dvojica-kineza-u-imotskom-pjevaju-navijacke-i-uzvikuju-za-dom-spremni-policija-privela-43-godisnjaka-iz-kine-i-60-godisnjeg-hrvata&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2Bchw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=cfe9e6c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://slobodnadalmacija.hr/dalmacija/split-zupanija/clanak/id/587269/drustvenim-mrezama-siri-se-snimka-na-kojoj-dvojica-kineza-u-imotskom-pjevaju-navijacke-i-uzvikuju-za-dom-spremni-policija-privela-43-godisnjaka-iz-kine-i-60-godisnjeg-hrvata</a><br />\n<br />\n條片喺克羅地亞人之間whatsapp傳得好犀利，但好多人都當笑片咁睇，以為個中國人只係南部Peljesac Bridge嘅地盤佬跟當地人學唱足球歌同嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （以為佢係地盤佬因為條橋個project判左俾大陸集團做，詳細可以wiki Peljesac Bridge，有中英文版）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://slobodnadalmacija.hr/bbimagehandler.ashx?file=/Portals/0/Images/2019/02/07/kinez00.jpg&amp;width=780\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslobodnadalmacija.hr%2Fbbimagehandler.ashx%3Ffile%3D%2FPortals%2F0%2FImages%2F2019%2F02%2F07%2Fkinez00.jpg%26width%3D780&h=46392bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而尋日同一媒體出左篇痴線佬嘅專訪，簡介話佢同一個十六歲香港𡃁仔喺Imotski租地方住左三個月，無業，其餘訪問內容都係同佢世界盃嗰陣噏嘅野三幅被。篇文其中一張相有show到裁決結果，話佢被cancel short-term stay，要喺判決生效後十日內離境再加三個月ban入境<br />\n<br />\n專訪+圖:<br />\n<a href=\"https://slobodnadalmacija.hr/dalmacija/split-zupanija/clanak/id/588118/kinez-priveden-zbog-ustaskog-pozdrava-sokirao-nas-je-pricom-u-imotski-smo-dosli-iskljucivo-zbog-ustasa-lani-sam-tetovirao-za-dom-spremni-a-sad-me-deportiraju-iz-moje-hrvatske\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslobodnadalmacija.hr%2Fdalmacija%2Fsplit-zupanija%2Fclanak%2Fid%2F588118%2Fkinez-priveden-zbog-ustaskog-pozdrava-sokirao-nas-je-pricom-u-imotski-smo-dosli-iskljucivo-zbog-ustasa-lani-sam-tetovirao-za-dom-spremni-a-sad-me-deportiraju-iz-moje-hrvatske&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2Bchw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=57597b45\" target=\"_blank\">https://slobodnadalmacija.hr/dalmacija/split-zupanija/clanak/id/588118/kinez-priveden-zbog-ustaskog-pozdrava-sokirao-nas-je-pricom-u-imotski-smo-dosli-iskljucivo-zbog-ustasa-lani-sam-tetovirao-za-dom-spremni-a-sad-me-deportiraju-iz-moje-hrvatske</a><br />\n<br />\n呢單野可能會成為唔太識香港嘅克羅地亞人對香港嘅第一印象<br />\n希望喺克羅地亞住/玩嘅香港人唔會因為咁成為當地人笑柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4255f85b89c3d8a99f137e28a7fbc216c154346","tid":1012795,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:53:15.000Z","msg":"正正經經響香港介紹下d波咪算<br />\n第一次走去克羅地亞就搞到比人驅逐出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e8efae5f69e5b07953390602988aae32ff9e68","tid":1012795,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"塞爾維亞又迫害我地"},{"pid":"73c3e81d7dd8f6fb876ef316944b8723ccbb68ab","tid":1012795,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0239200091ee19eb7ecb69a7bce0a89657ce62","tid":1012795,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"(突發)太宰二係克羅地亞比人拉鳩咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1005405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1005405</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"859f9efe50620bf624d0f0541acd043755dd18a8","tid":1012795,"uid":21061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"佢講到當地市民好撐佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be942cef20216e7c370d194ecdaeb4977fe3b10e","tid":1012795,"uid":196258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"859f9efe50620bf624d0f0541acd043755dd18a8","tid":1012795,"uid":21061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"佢講到當地市民好撐佢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:21:18.000Z","msg":"只能話佢識揀地方搞事，Imotski嘅人本身都比較法西斯。如果佢真係堅揪又夠薑嘅點解唔直接去大城巿宣揚佢所謂&quot;全克羅地亞都撐&quot;嘅訊息？<br />\n<br />\n頭先search返先見到個痴線佬尋日有開post&quot;克羅地亞尋根之旅取得成果 ，克羅地亞國會議員發言聲援&quot;。Post左一大段野話自己嘅行動喚醒當地人民族意識又乜又物。Click入條link睇，篇文其實係講緊該議員喺國會講埋啲三姑六婆野（i.e. 癡肥問題同埋條痴線佬）而非討論正經重要議題。仲要個議員其實唔係講緊民族意識，只係輕輕帶過話希望當局可以放返條痴線佬同祝國內嘅中國人豬年快樂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日鳩post克羅地亞文歌詞口號吹到自己好似土生土長克羅地亞人咁，睇返條片咪又係用英文同人溝通，當地語言都未識就學人玩種族主義。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頂樓篇專訪都有話佢已經第三次喺Imotski俾人拉（入境三個月之間），如果佢唔好彩俾人永久blacklist禁止入境就好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f200f2cf1f814fe08c93b2dfb38c8b50d84d4c","tid":1012795,"uid":21061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"平時見到貼果d野搞到我以為佢真係識克語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n持平d講佢貼足球資訊係ok既 我一直有睇佢係discuss d post 到佢係兩登開post <br />\n但佢華人身份支持克國種族主義就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日半夜三更去合和克國大使館鳩叫<br />\n仲要FF自己同克羅地亞既connection 幾咁深厚<br />\n唔知以為塞爾維亞人有份殺佢全家<br />\n但跟本未去過當地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fca7180b75387c477fc282b7c59b182a859114","tid":1012795,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:58:14.000Z","msg":"太宰真係夠鐘返青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd62d0617a4d52a5a526321ac86c2616bd1ec86","tid":1012795,"uid":196258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f200f2cf1f814fe08c93b2dfb38c8b50d84d4c","tid":1012795,"uid":21061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:53:18.000Z","msg":"平時見到貼果d野搞到我以為佢真係識克語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n持平d講佢貼足球資訊係ok既 我一直有睇佢係discuss d post 到佢係兩登開post <br />\n但佢華人身份支持克國種族主義就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日半夜三更去合和克國大使館鳩叫<br />\n仲要FF自己同克羅地亞既connection 幾咁深厚<br />\n唔知以為塞爾維亞人有份殺佢全家<br />\n但跟本未去過當地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"我都佩服佢身在香港但咁熱衷同熟悉克羅地亞歷史，只不過意識停留咗喺上世紀。我覺得部份Imotski居民&quot;支持&quot;佢係因為佢好似小丑咁做左啲當地法西斯唔可以公開聲大大咁做嘅野<br />\n<br />\n要睇當地人睇法嘅話，小弟嘅克羅地亞同屋朋友話某程度上都理解到佢心態，因為Croats/Serbs vs 香港/大陸，唔同嘅係而家克羅地亞同塞爾維亞已經各自有自己國家，所以普遍嚟講果種仇恨都跟住慢慢減弱（當然極右份子仍然存在，當權政黨HDZ都係右派）。雖然兩邊人民各自圍內都仲會攞啲口號嚟講笑，但如果出到其他國家遇到問題佢地會企同一陣線"}]}